code: /**  * Increment the current count by 1.  */ @Override public void inc() {     count++. }

comment: /**  * Increment the current count by the given value.  *  * @param n value to increment the current count by  */
code: /**  * Increment the current count by the given value.  *  * @param n value to increment the current count by  */ @Override public void inc(long n) {     count += n. }
/**  * Decrement the current count by 1.  */ @Override public void dec() {     count--. }

comment: /**  * Decrement the current count by the given value.  *  * @param n value to decrement the current count by  */
code: /**  * Decrement the current count by the given value.  *  * @param n value to decrement the current count by  */ @Override public void dec(long n) {     count -= n. }

comment: /**  * Returns the current count.  *  * @return current count  */
code: /**  * Returns the current count.  *  * @return current count  */ @Override public long getCount() {     return count. }
